  "story": {
    "html": "<span class=\"text-chip\" data-kind=\"phase\" data-phase-id=\"phase-arrival\">Arrival Phase</span>\n<p>The storyboard starts at <span class=\"text-chip\" data-kind=\"poi\" data-poi-id=\"poi-origin\" data-poi-lat=\"33.755\" data-poi-lon=\"-84.39\">Origin Plaza</span>, then opens image <span class=\"text-chip text-chip--media\" data-kind=\"image\" data-media-id=\"media-image\" data-url=\"./data/media/images/media-image.png\" data-title=\"Gallery Image\" data-description=\"Image chip description\">Gallery Image</span> and model <span class=\"text-chip text-chip--media\" data-kind=\"model\" data-media-id=\"media-model\" data-url=\"./data/media/models/media-model.glb\" data-title=\"Gallery Model\">Gallery Model</span> evidence.</p>\n<h2><span class=\"text-chip\" data-kind=\"phase\" data-phase-id=\"phase-media-lab\">Media Lab Phase</span></h2>\n<p>At <span class=\"text-chip\" data-kind=\"poi\" data-poi-id=\"poi-media-lab\" data-poi-lat=\"33.756\" data-poi-lon=\"-84.391\">Media Lab</span>, test video <span class=\"text-chip text-chip--media\" data-kind=\"video\" data-media-id=\"media-video\" data-url=\"./data/media/videos/media-video.mp4\" data-title=\"Gallery Video\">Gallery Video</span>, sound <span class=\"text-chip text-chip--media\" data-kind=\"sound\" data-media-id=\"media-audio\" data-url=\"./data/media/audio/media-audio.mp3\" data-title=\"Gallery Audio\">Gallery Audio</span>, document <span class=\"text-chip text-chip--media\" data-kind=\"document\" data-media-id=\"media-document\" data-url=\"./data/media/documents/media-document.pdf\" data-title=\"Gallery PDF\">Gallery PDF</span>, link <span class=\"text-chip text-chip--link\" data-kind=\"link\" data-url=\"https://example.com/rich-pwa-smoke\">Reference Link</span>, and time <span class=\"text-chip text-chip--time\" data-kind=\"time\" data-time=\"1945-05-08T12:00\">1945 marker</span>.</p>",
    "text": "Arrival Phase. The storyboard starts at Origin Plaza and uses every published media chip type. Media Lab Phase tests video, audio, document, link, and time chips.",
